Hi guy,
after a while aim_ak-colt gets boring because it is always the same, so I came up with the idea of making the for pilons breakable and here you go, a map that changes every round, no round is the same and there are a lot more tactics that you can use like storming and shooting through the pilon. If you like this map dont hesitate to put it on your server to give it a fresh kick, 
thx to all
